[
    {
        "text": "Hello! Welcome to Michael's Better Business English.",
        "startTime": 700,
        "endTime": 3783,
        "slowStartTime": 1200,
        "slowEndTime": 5900
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at a difficult but important topic in business:...",
        "startTime": 4433,
        "endTime": 8317,
        "slowStartTime": 6800,
        "slowEndTime": 12700
    },
    {
        "text": "...How to apologize politely.",
        "startTime": 8767,
        "endTime": 11050,
        "slowStartTime": 13300,
        "slowEndTime": 16800
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, this is a very difficult area for many Japanese business people...",
        "startTime": 12033,
        "endTime": 15850,
        "slowStartTime": 18200,
        "slowEndTime": 24000
    },
    {
        "text": "...because it's very different culture to culture.",
        "startTime": 16333,
        "endTime": 20050,
        "slowStartTime": 24650,
        "slowEndTime": 30300
    },
    {
        "text": "Traditional Japanese polite style, meaning uses lots of polite language and bowing...",
        "startTime": 20917,
        "endTime": 26417,
        "slowStartTime": 31525,
        "slowEndTime": 39850
    },
    {
        "text": "...but it's quite different than say, Western style.",
        "startTime": 26767,
        "endTime": 29117,
        "slowStartTime": 40300,
        "slowEndTime": 43900
    },
    {
        "text": "In countries such as America or Germany, apologizing is usually used rarely...",
        "startTime": 29967,
        "endTime": 35383,
        "slowStartTime": 45100,
        "slowEndTime": 53300
    },
    {
        "text": "...and to indicate accepting personal responsibility.",
        "startTime": 35867,
        "endTime": 39083,
        "slowStartTime": 53950,
        "slowEndTime": 58850
    },
    {
        "text": "So, you need to be careful when and how should you apologize...",
        "startTime": 39800,
        "endTime": 44034,
        "slowStartTime": 59850,
        "slowEndTime": 66276
    },
    {
        "text": "...when working with people from different cultures.",
        "startTime": 44153,
        "endTime": 46950,
        "slowStartTime": 66379,
        "slowEndTime": 70650
    },
    {
        "text": "Some advice to help you in general though, when apologizing to Western business people.",
        "startTime": 48167,
        "endTime": 53217,
        "slowStartTime": 72400,
        "slowEndTime": 80050
    },
    {
        "text": "Use these four steps.",
        "startTime": 54167,
        "endTime": 56117,
        "slowStartTime": 81400,
        "slowEndTime": 84400
    },
    {
        "text": "First, apologize.",
        "startTime": 56900,
        "endTime": 58850,
        "slowStartTime": 85500,
        "slowEndTime": 88500
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"We are so sorry for the delay of the delivery.\"",
        "startTime": 59633,
        "endTime": 63117,
        "slowStartTime": 89600,
        "slowEndTime": 94900
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, give a clear reason for the problem.",
        "startTime": 64233,
        "endTime": 67283,
        "slowStartTime": 96500,
        "slowEndTime": 101150
    },
    {
        "text": "\"This was due to a mistake in our factory.\"",
        "startTime": 68433,
        "endTime": 70850,
        "slowStartTime": 102800,
        "slowEndTime": 106500
    },
    {
        "text": "Third, make an action clear that you will take in order to avoid the problem from happening again.",
        "startTime": 72133,
        "endTime": 78583,
        "slowStartTime": 108350,
        "slowEndTime": 118100
    },
    {
        "text": "Example, \"We are changing our factory production schedule to avoid any future delays.\"",
        "startTime": 79733,
        "endTime": 85983,
        "slowStartTime": 119750,
        "slowEndTime": 129199
    },
    {
        "text": "And then finally, apologize again.",
        "startTime": 87033,
        "endTime": 88983,
        "slowStartTime": 130699,
        "slowEndTime": 133699
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Again, we'd like to apologize for this accident.\"",
        "startTime": 89833,
        "endTime": 92983,
        "slowStartTime": 134900,
        "slowEndTime": 139700
    },
    {
        "text": "Use these four steps for a polite, clear, and effective apology.",
        "startTime": 94667,
        "endTime": 99317,
        "slowStartTime": 142150,
        "slowEndTime": 149200
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck!",
        "startTime": 100200,
        "endTime": 101583,
        "slowStartTime": 150450,
        "slowEndTime": 152600
    }
]